abstract: NHL Roundup; Minnesota Wild beat New York Islanders, 2-1; other hockey news noted.
lead_paragraph: Zach Parise scored a tying goal in the third period and then scored the only goal in a shootout as Minnesota earned a 10th consecutive road win.

headline.main: Parise Gives Wild All They Need to Top the Islanders
